abstract. Read through the physical paper
and once ready hit the Read button to earn

25
00:03:37,500 --> 00:03:44,500
15 points. Note how the button changed from
orange to green to mark a state of completion.

26
00:03:45,830 --> 00:03:50,900
Navigating back to the main menu, it can be
seen how the total and daily points increased

27
