the points earned. If for example 1000 words
from the Introduction chapter are written,

42
00:05:23,910 --> 00:05:30,910
points can be earned by sliding the slider
to the left. This increases the word count

43
00:05:31,660 --> 00:05:36,990
found beneath the slider and changes the colour
of the buttons. Navigating back to the main

44
00:05:36,990 --> 00:05:43,990
menu, it can be seen how the total and daily
points increased to reflect the points earned.

45
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:52,060
Now Let's explore the Evaluation.
Click the Evaluation screen to display the

46
00:05:52,060 --> 00:05:59,060
